                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9165" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2294</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">819 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“封闭内陆”到“开放前沿”：天山脚下的中国葡萄酒庄</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Closed Inland&quot; to &quot;Open Frontier&quot;: A Chinese Vineyard at the Foot of the Tianshan Mountains</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王皓， 赵婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对外经济贸易大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新疆天塞酒庄有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天塞酒庄；一带一路；生态经济；文化创新；品牌国际化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tiansai Vineyard, Belt and Road Initiative, ecological economy, cultural innovation, brand internationalization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例讲述了天塞酒庄如何抓住“一带一路”倡议的机遇，通过生态经济模式、文化创新和数字赋能，将新疆戈壁滩改造成现代化葡萄酒庄。酒庄以“呈现自然之美”为核心理念，通过种植5万棵杨树和天山雪水滴灌技术，改善生态环境，推动绿色农业和有机种植，同时坚持“最少干预”的自然酿造方式，酿造出独特的中国风味葡萄酒。在文化创新方面，天塞酒庄推出生肖酒和节气系列，将中国传统文化与酿酒工艺深度结合，成功打造出具有差异化竞争力的品牌形象。此外，酒庄通过数字化转型和文旅融合，吸引了年轻消费群体的关注，并积极拓展“一带一路”框架下的国际市场，多次获得国际大奖，展现了中国品牌的文化自信。本案例展示了天塞酒庄在生态经济、文化创新和国际化战略中的成功实践，为企业战略管理和品牌建设提供了重要启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case study explores how Tiansai Vineyard utilized the &quot;Belt and Road Initiative&quot; to transform the Gobi Desert in Xinjiang into a modern vineyard through ecological economy, cultural innovation, and digital transformation. Guided by the philosophy of &quot;showcasing the beauty of nature,&quot; the vineyard improved the local ecosystem by planting 50,000 poplars and adopting drip irrigation with Tianshan snowmelt, promoting green agriculture and organic farming. Its &quot;minimal intervention&quot; approach produces wines with a distinctive Chinese flavor. By integrating Chinese traditions with winemaking through Zodiac-themed wines and solar term series, Tiansai created a unique brand identity. Digital transformation and wine tourism further attracted younger consumers, while international awards and expansion under the &quot;Belt and Road&quot; framework established Tiansai as a globally recognized Chinese wine brand.This case demonstrates Tiansai Vineyard&#39;s achievements in sustainability, cultural innovation, and global strategy, providing insights into strategic management and brand building.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PESTEL分析模型; 五种力量的模型; SWOT分析模型; 核心竞争力理论; 资源基础理论; 企业持续竞争优势理论; 利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
